Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Erica, has stated her position on finding love on the reality television show. The BBNaija housemate stressed that she’s not on the show to look for love. Erica disclosed this during her diary session with Biggie, on Monday. “I’m not looking for love right now.,” Erica told Biggie. Erica is currently in what could be described as a relationship with fellow housemate, Kiddwaya, despite having feelings for Laycon. She, however, rejected Laycon’s advances, claiming she is only mentally attracted to him.